text: Iteyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Iteyevsky Selsoviet, Ilishevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 506 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 13 km from Verkhneyarkeyevoh. == References == Category:Rural localities in Ilishevsky District Category:Ufa Governorate
